chart.name: Disk IOPs
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.write.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b') and filter('stat', 'sum'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.read.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Disk I/O Bytes/Operation
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.disk.io.write.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b')).sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('^aws.ec2.disk.io.read.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b')).sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.write.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b')).sum().publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.read.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b')).sum().publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (A/C).publish(label='E')
F = (B/D).publish(label='F')

chart.name: CPU % Trend
chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.cpu.utilization', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).publish(label='A')

B = data('^aws.ec2.network.io.transmit.total', filter=filter('InstanceId', 'i-e8b1df4b'), extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).mean().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.network.io.transmit.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Top Instances by CPU %
chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.cpu.utilization', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).mean(by=['AWSUniqueId']).top(count=5).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Top Network Bytes Out/Min
chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.network.io.transmit.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).mean(by=['InstanceId']).top(count=5).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Disk Ops
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.write.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('^aws.ec2.disk.ops.read.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Disk I/O Bytes
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.disk.io.write.total', rollup='sum', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('^aws.ec2.disk.io.read.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Disk Metrics 24h Growth %
chart.programText:
A = data('Disk*', filter=filter('namespace', 'AWS/EC2') and filter('InstanceId', '*') and filter('stat', 'sum'), rollup='rate', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B - 1).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Network Bytes Out vs. 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('^aws.ec2.network.io.transmit.total', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).sum().mean(over='1h').publish(label='A')
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Active Hosts by AZ
chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.cpu.utilization', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).max(over='1h').count(by=['aws_availability_zone']).publish(label='A')

chart.name: Active Hosts
chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.cpu.utilization', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).max(over='1h').count().publish(label='A')

chart.name: Network Bytes In vs. 24h Change %

C = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B/C-1).scale(100).publish(label='D')

chart.programText: A = data('^aws.ec2.cpu.utilization', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=5).mean(by=['aws_image_id']).top(count=5).publish(label='A')
